data.name: DateTimeRange
desc: represents a range of date+time values.

items.name: EndDay
lines: contains the end day of month (1-31 or 0 for a void date) for the range.

items.name: EndHours
lines: contains the end hour (0-23) for the range.

items.name: EndMinutes
lines: contains the end minutes (0-59) for the range.

items.name: EndMonth
lines: contains the end month of year (1-12 or 0 for a void date) for the range.

items.name: EndNanoSeconds
lines: contains the end nanoseconds (0 - 999 999 999) for the range.

items.name: EndSeconds
lines: contains the end seconds (0-59) for the range.

items.name: EndYear
lines: contains the end year for the range.

items.name: IsUTC
lines: true: time zone is UTC false: unknown time zone.

items.name: StartDay
lines: contains the start day of month (1-31 or 0 for a void date) for the range.

items.name: StartHours
lines: contains the start hour (0-23) for the range.

items.name: StartMinutes
lines: contains the start minutes (0-59) for the range.

items.name: StartMonth
lines: contains the start month of year (1-12 or 0 for a void date) for the range.

items.name: StartNanoSeconds
lines: contains the start nanoseconds (0 - 999 999 999) for the range.

items.name: StartSeconds
lines: contains the start seconds (0-59) for the range.

items.name: StartYear
lines: contains the start year for the range.
